---
title: Herby Italian Chicken with Pesto Pasta Salad and Asparagus
description: Juicy Italian pan-fried chicken with pasta and veggies tossed in creamy pesto. A meal for the whole family, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner or a backyard picnic!
